# PredictX Contract Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "User Interfaces"
        Frontend["Frontend Application"]
        CLI["Stellar CLI"]
    end

    subgraph "Smart Contracts"
        PM["PredictionMarket"]
        VO["VotingOracle"]
        Treasury["Treasury"]
        PF["PollFactory"]
    end

    subgraph "Soroban VM"
        Token["XLM / Stellar Asset Token"]
    end

    Frontend -->|"invoke()"| PM
    Frontend -->|"invoke()"| VO
    Frontend -->|"invoke()"| PF
    CLI -->|"invoke()"| PM
    CLI -->|"invoke()"| Treasury

    PM -->|"transfer()"| Token
    PM -->|"set_poll_status()"| VO
    PM -->|"get_poll_status()"| VO
    PM -->|"deposit()"| Treasury
```

## Contract Deployment Order

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin
    participant Token as Token (builtin)
    participant Treasury
    participant Oracle as VotingOracle
    participant PM as PredictionMarket

    Admin->>Token: Deploy Stellar Asset Contract
    Admin->>Treasury: Deploy + initialize()
    Admin->>Oracle: Deploy + initialize()
    Admin->>PM: Deploy + initialize(admin, oracle, token, treasury, fee)
```

## State Dependencies

```mermaid
graph LR
    PM["PredictionMarket"] --> VO["VotingOracle"]
    PM --> Treasury
    
    VO -.->|"stores status"| PollStatus["Per-Poll Status"]
    PM -.->|"stores"| Polls["Poll Data"]
    PM -.->|"stores"| Stakes["Stake Records"]
    PM -.->|"stores"| Matches["Match Data"]
```
